Author: Immortal / Divine
Version: 2.2
Requires: PowerShell 5.1+, .NET Framework 4.6.2+, Administrator privileges, Bypassed 32-bit PowerShell execution.


[Changelogs]
   - Added:
    - New Hotkey Manager in the settings to see and edit all current active Hotkeys
	- New interactive notification progress system for all features
	- Manual disconnect by right clicking the Terminate button
	- Remembers last position of dashboard
	- Redesigned the message windows for true dark mode
	- DataGrid Contextmenu:
	 - Set Hotkey to bring a set of saved clients to front
	 - Manual reposition of clients to a saved location
	 - Manual reconnect after disconnect
	- Worldboss Notification System through Discord (privat, pm for access)

   - Fixed:
	- Minimizes clients that timeout during login
	- Increased login/reconnect speed
	- Increased window detection to prevent false clicks during login
	- You can open the profile location by double clicking the path now
	- Ftool key settings were not being saved, fixed
	- Ftool positioning fixed when window not focused
	- Removed the initial wait time of an Ftool instance for start. It now starts instant.

   - More:
	- Code cleanup

